</quantity>
, a mountainous area covered with a mixture of gravel and clay, in the Irano-Turanian floristic region (
<bibRefCitation author="TAKHTAJAN A. L." box="[819,979,501,525]" pageId="3" pageNumber="32" refId="ref3038" refString="TAKHTAJAN A. L. 1986. - Floristic Regions of the World. University of California Press, Berkeley, Los Angeles, London, 522 p." type="book" year="1986">Takhtajan 1986</bibRefCitation>
)
